    • Field Detail

      • personality

        public int personality
        The personality of the call. The personality indicates whether this user originated this call or this call was placed to the user.

        Possible values:

        0 - BroadWorks Originator

        1 - Originator

        2 - Terminator

      • state

        public int state
        The state of the call.

        Possible values:

        0 - idle

        1 - alerting

        2 - active

        3 - held

        4 - remote held

        5 - released

        6 - detached

        7 - client alerting

      • releaseCause

        public int releaseCause
        The release cause of the call. This tag has meaning when the call is released. Until then, it has a default value of “0” that can be ignored.

      • remoteNumber

        public java.lang.String remoteNumber
        The remote phone number in the call.

      • remoteName

        public java.lang.String remoteName
        The remote name (if available) in the call.

      • callType

        public int callType
        The call type for this call leg.

        0 - unknown

        1 - intra-group

        2 - enterprise

        3 - network

        4 - network URL

        5 - emergency

        6 - repair

        7 - error

        8 - city-wide centrex

        9 - private dial plan
